claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common

Class XtypeTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common.Xnode
      • claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common.XtypeTable

  • public class XtypeTable
extends Xnode
    The XtypeTable represents the typeTable (3.1) element in XcodeML intermediate representation. Elements: ( FbasicType | FfunctionType | FstructType ) * - Optional: - FbasicType (FbasicType) - FfunctionType (FfunctionType) - FstructType (FstructType)
    Author:
    clementval
